            "title": "伊朗拒絕特朗普談判提議 美以伊三方空襲與軍事對峙持續升級",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"伊朗拒絕特朗普談判提議 美以伊三方空襲與軍事對峙持續升級\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5HXvszSK.fUmK1m0bE40oQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/04b1c5e0-264e-11f1-bb7f-f06fab2a185d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">伊朗拒絕特朗普談判提議 美以伊三方空襲與軍事對峙持續升級</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%8F%90%E8%AD%B0-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BB%A5%E4%BC%8A%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E7%A9%BA%E8%A5%B2%E8%88%87%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-070005597.html",
